imdb.plot outline: All is well in Pepe De jesus' family until his father is found dead, apparently murdered by thhe arrow that Pepe owned since childhood. Pepe is then blamed and wrongfully convicted for the death of his own father. While in transit to his prison, the vehicle carrying Pepe is bombed and falls from a bridge. Pepe luckily survived and was later found by Venus, who later on teaches him martrial arts. Everyone thought that Pepe was dead.
imdb.title: Alyas Robin Hood
plot: All is well in Pepe De jesus' family until his father is found dead, apparently murdered by thhe arrow that Pepe owned since childhood. Pepe is then blamed and wrongfully convicted for the death of his own father. While in transit to his prison, the vehicle carrying Pepe is bombed and falls from a bridge. Pepe luckily survived and was later found by Venus, who later on teaches him martrial arts. Everyone thought that Pepe was dead.
